snippet.title: Neyyah Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Neyyah now: https://bit.ly/3PFY79V

Find out more at:
https://www.microprose.com/games/neyyah/
https://discord.gg/xyWqGak

Neyyah is a 2D slideshow first-person point-and-click adventure puzzle game from solo developer, Aaron Gwynaire. You are thrown into a strange secretive world called Neyyah. Use careful observation and logic to uncover the mysteries entwined within Neyyah's peculiar landscapes and bizarre cultures.
